        <section>
            <title>Northern Sámi as input languge in Windows</title>

            <p>We will show how to set up Northern Sámi as input languge. When Northern Sámi set up as the input language, the spell checker will automatically be switched to Northern Sámi when the Divvun tools have been installed.</p>

            <ol>
                <li>Go to <strong>Start</strong>, write <strong>control panel</strong>, open <strong>Control Panel</strong>
                    <p><img src="images/win8_start_en.png" alt="Start" /></p>
                </li>
                <li>Below the heading <strong>Clock, Language, and Region</strong>, press <strong>Add a language</strong>.
                    <p><img src="images/win8_kontrollpanel_en.png" alt="Control Panel"/></p>
                </li>
                <li>Press <strong>Add a language</strong>.
                    <p><img src="images/win8_sprak_en.png" alt="Language" /></p>
                </li>
                <li>Choose <strong>Northern Sami</strong>. Press <strong>Open</strong>
                    <p><img src="images/win8_legg_til_sprak_sme_en.png" alt="Add languages"/></p>
                </li>
                <li>Choose <strong>Northern Sami</strong>. Press <strong>Legg till</strong>.
                    <p><img src="images/win8_regionale_varianter_sme_en.png" alt="Regionale varianter"/></p>
                </li>
                <li><em>Tasturoppsett:+Norsk+med+samisk</em> olgešbealde: Press <strong>Alternativer</strong>
                    <p><img src="images/win8_sprak_sme_alternativer_en.png" alt="Språk etter å ha valgt nordsamisk"/></p>
                </li>
                <li>Choose <strong>Legg til en inndatametode</strong>
                    <p>
                        <img src="images/win8_sprakalternativer_sme_en.png" alt="Språkalternativer"/>
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>Choose <strong>Samisk, utvidet Norge</strong>. Press <strong>Legg til</strong>
                    <p>
                        <img src="images/win8_inndatametode_sme_en.png" alt="Inndatametode"/>
                    </p>
                </li>
				<li><em>Norsk med samisk</em> olgešbealde: Press <strong>Fjern</strong>, then <strong>Save</strong>
                    <p>
                        <img src="images/win8_sprak_fjern_norsk_med_samisk_sme_en.png" alt="Språkalternativer: Fjern norsk med samisk"/>
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>De dus lea <strong>davvisámegiella (Norga)</strong> čállingiellan ja <strong>Samisk, utvidet Norge</strong> čállinvuohkin.
                    <p>
                        <img src="images/win8_sprak_ferdig_sme_en.png" alt="Språk med nordsamisk ferdigvalgt"/>
                    </p>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </section>
